Section 1:
Act 161 of the Regular Session
1 State of Arkansas
A Bill
2 95th General Assembly
3 Regular Session, 2025 HOUSE BILL 1418
4
5 By: Representative Joey Carr
6 By: Senator Rice
7
For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT TO PROHIBIT LOCAL GOVERNMENT REGULATION OF
10 KNIVES OR KNIFE-MAKING COMPONENTS; AND FOR OTHER
11 PURPOSES.
12
13
Subtitle
14
15 TO PROHIBIT LOCAL GOVERNMENT REGULATION
16 OF KNIVES OR KNIFE-MAKING COMPONENTS.
17
18 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
19
20 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code ยง 14-16-504(b)(1)(A), concerning the
21 regulation of firearms and ammunition by local government, is amended to read
22 as follows:
23 (b)(1)(A) Except as otherwise provided in state or federal law, A a
24 local unit of government shall not enact any an ordinance or regulation
25 pertaining to, or regulate in any other manner, the ownership, transfer,
26 transportation, carrying, or possession of:
27 (i) firearms, Firearms;
28 (ii) ammunition Ammunition for firearms,;
29 (iii) or components Components of firearms,;
30 (iv) Knives; or
31 (v) Knife-making components except as otherwise
32 provided in state or federal law.
33
34 SECTION 2. Arkansas Code ยง 14-54-1411(b)(1)(A), concerning the
35 regulation of firearms and ammunition by local government, is amended to read
36 as follows:
